{"tid":1777103,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"還錢呀頂你！！","createTime":"2019-12-10T03:51:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T04:53:20.000Z","uid":311244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0342c6c9065fec2d2b29096526f3a994c9164a9f","tid":1777103,"uid":311244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:51:19.000Z","msg":"某位手足，因為我見你過去幫過我，你依家問我借1000應急用，我決定借比你，但你唔單單唔準時還，到依家仲未還比我，因為我借你1000我差d要食樹皮食西北風！到我要應急揾你還錢你又一直拖，我當你係手足，你係咪當我係老奉？如果連誠信都冇，仲有咩資格講核彈都唔割呀！！ BTW再唔還就老豆揾仔見"},{"pid":"0940ae9e2f2841c2838569271296d0d2996e939b","tid":1777103,"uid":213163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:52:21.000Z","msg":"仲有7個鐘就係啦... 跪求大家入嚟睇一睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1777075\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1777075</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hy3vV3M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHy3vV3M.jpg&h=7e318a13&s={SIZE}\" />唔好意思借個位嚟<br />\n好重要今晚就係啦！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n*已獲不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n~~~~~~~<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【國際人權日．正日集會】</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1948年12月10日，聯合國公佈《世界人權宣言》，確立生而為人的基本權利。走過71年，世界人權仍然是未竟之路。在香港及世界各地，人民仍要為爭取基本的自由及權利奮鬥，甚至有所付出及犧牲。<br />\n<br />\n12月10日晚，我們一起站出來，為香港人加油，也為全球為人權奮鬥的人打氣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">日期：12月10日<br />\n時間：18:30-22:00<br />\n地點：金鐘連儂牆下<br />\n</span><br />\n內容：<br />\n悼念及回顧<br />\n嘉賓講話<br />\n短片欣賞及分享<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LCPK0vx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLCPK0vx.jpg&h=63585984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n推呀屌你再過7個鐘就係啦 唔好再屌鬼啦行動post呢文宣post呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係完咗人權日遊行就end game㗎<br />\n我地仲有訴求㗎！！！<br />\n一陣要見到連儂牆有十萬人呀！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n12月10號 6點半政總見！！"},{"pid":"15750d33cec976b7c93e74bb0e549ba62adf1194","tid":1777103,"uid":213163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:52:36.000Z","msg":"欠債還錢 天公地道"},{"pid":"ca7feb6ea7148a89dcb23a7ae55b385c51ccf539","tid":1777103,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:53:23.000Z","msg":"貼相貼名貼detail係基本常識吧"},{"pid":"4dffdee1168240e17a7b1bdfba4c08be6bd16a1b","tid":1777103,"uid":108269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:53:25.000Z","msg":"有幾多人借過錢但仲未還？"},{"pid":"b4dc7d6d27417607c6f8e2791ec148289d6a8878","tid":1777103,"uid":172427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:54:14.000Z","msg":"1k 好多人幫到你<br />\n請你信任一路行落來嘅手足"},{"pid":"75476fdde43723cbf8380c9e0c5df9a9cc404c02","tid":1777103,"uid":316537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:54:35.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"78b90eef1b0ae61382fd95d97c6c240353865540","tid":1777103,"uid":222907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HgGQWsT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHgGQWsT.jpg&h=ea9f429f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"029de4729a184ad120c6f308ca0b3e0a55826169","tid":1777103,"uid":172427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78b90eef1b0ae61382fd95d97c6c240353865540","tid":1777103,"uid":222907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HgGQWsT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHgGQWsT.jpg&h=ea9f429f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:57:30.000Z","msg":"中国移動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下次請專業小小唔該"},{"pid":"b30abb045bfb40130a741876c07fdbf80653d981","tid":1777103,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"029de4729a184ad120c6f308ca0b3e0a55826169","tid":1777103,"uid":172427,"like"